I was so disappointed of the service I received last night. The Security Guard was very rude at the entrance. When we walk in no one directed us to a table. We asked the waitress if it was ok to sit at a table, she said yes and then moments later another woman very rudely asked us to sit at another table. After this we noticed an man who seemed to work there complaining about us taking up too much space. We were only three people. The drinks took about 20 minutes and food took over 30 minutes. The food was a bit salty and the drink didn’t even make it to half the cup. In the end when we asked the waitress for the check it took her over 20 minutes to bring to us. Never going there again.
